Key Usage Examples of Netsh:
View IP Settings: netsh interface ip show config.
Reset TCP/IP Stack: netsh int ip reset (used to fix network connectivity issues).
Manage Wi-Fi Profiles: netsh wlan show profiles to list saved networks, or netsh wlan show profile name="NetworkName" key=clear to see Wi-Fi passwords.
Set Static IP Address: netsh interface ip set address "Local Area Connection" static 192.168.1.10 255.255.255.0 192.168.1.1.
Reset Winsock Catalog: netsh winsock reset (fixes socket errors).
Configure Firewall: netsh advfirewall set...
